a pretty wide range
of institutions

248
00:18:26,714 --> 00:18:29,586
that showed that
these attackers were...
were quite busy.

249
00:18:29,673 --> 00:18:32,111
There was huge pickup
in the media.
It was all over the world.

250
00:18:38,726 --> 00:18:42,382
