00:37:26,809 --> 00:37:29,377
[Silva] It was good
in the first two or three times

487
00:37:29,464 --> 00:37:31,814
in more calm demonstrations.

488
00:37:31,901 --> 00:37:34,295
I remember
there was a discussion,
and then Carioca said,

489
00:37:34,382 --> 00:37:37,994
"No, I found an app.

490
00:37:38,081 --> 00:37:40,823
Its name is TwitCasting
